<p><span class="headline text-highlight">Completely free</span><br>
No in-game purchases, no "pay to win", no microtransactions. You don't even have to log in or make an account to play.</p>

<p><span class="headline text-highlight">Minimal micromanagement</span><br>
Simulation games need depth, but they need the right amount of depth with a UI to help you make sense of it. We seek to avoid mandatory micromanagement as much as possible. Video games should be fun, not tedious.</p>
